name: No Coast
description: Total running time of 6 minutes / 6 seconds / 6 milliseconds - Minted as part of the #HEN666 in June 2021.- 100% Live performance and recording by Aevin, using the Make Noise 0-Coast synthesizer, creating an infinite soundscape in remembrance and respect to the pioneers of electronic music. This is (probably) one of the longest in duration objects currently minted on the platform; as for the time of minting the file size limit is 30MB. The video bitrate was significantly reduced to less than 1 Mbps, as well as the audio quality to 64Kbps. The collector of this will receive on request the original video which is slightly longer in time, and it is 600mb+ in size.
